       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    ARI80102.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA ARI80102.
      *
      *     Utilizadores
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE ARI80102         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE ARCD0103 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE ARCD2000 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY ARCV8010.
       COPY ARCV8011.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY ARCK0001.
       COPY ARCK0002.
       COPY VIAL0015.
      *
       COPY ARCL2505.
       COPY ETCL0002.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            VARIAVEIS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 AUX-CPERFIL            PIC X(12).
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-ARVT0100 PIC X(08) VALUE 'ARVT0100'.
           05 CON-ARVT2000 PIC X(08) VALUE 'ARVT2000'.
           05 WS-PROGNAME  PIC  X(08) VALUE 'ARI80102'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE ARI80102         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *
       COPY VIAL0004.
      *
            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.
      *
           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
                 THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
      *
       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.
      *
           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO ARCV8010-MSG.
           MOVE ARCV8010-ASE               TO ARCV8011-ASE.
           MOVE ARCV8010-ADE               TO ARCV8011-ADE.
      *
           IF NOT VIAL0001-CRIACAO
      * Obtem master do perfil do utilizador logado
              IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 PERFORM 1200-OBT-MASTER-USER
                    THRU 1200-OBT-MASTER-USER-EXIT
              END-IF

      * Obtem master do user introduzido de input
              IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 PERFORM 1300-OBT-MASTER-PERFIL
                    THRU 1300-OBT-MASTER-PERFIL-EXIT
              END-IF

      *Valida se ambos os perfis tęm o mesmo master
      *Compara se aux-perfil (master do user logado) é igual
      *ao ARCL2505-CPERFILMAST que é o master do perfil de input

              IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 IF AUX-CPERFIL NOT EQUAL TO ARCL2505-CPERFILMAST
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO ARCV8011-CPERFIL-S
                    MOVE ARCK0001-PERFIL-INVA
                      TO ARCV8011-CPERFIL-MSG
                    MOVE ARCK0002-CAPLIC-AR
                      TO ARCV8011-CPERFIL-CAPLIC
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   1200-OBT-MASTER-USER
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1200-OBT-MASTER-USER.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1200-OBT-MASTER-USER'  TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'VIAL0001-CUTILIZA-I '  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  VIAL0001-CUTILIZA-I    TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           INITIALIZE ARCL2505-COMMAREA REPLACING NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                             ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES.

           SET ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS TO TRUE.


           MOVE VIAL0001-CUTILIZA-I        TO ARCL2505-CUSERID.

           CALL ARCL2505-ROTINA USING ETCL0002-COMMAREA
                                      ARCL2505-COMMAREA.
           IF ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
              MOVE ARCL2505-CPERFILMAST TO AUX-CPERFIL
           ELSE
              MOVE ETCL0002-IND-ERROS
                TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                TO ARCV8011-CPERFIL-S
              MOVE ETCL0002-NR-ERRO
                TO ARCV8011-CPERFIL-MSG
              MOVE ARCK0002-CAPLIC-AR
                TO ARCV8011-CPERFIL-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

       1200-OBT-MASTER-USER-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   1300-OBT-MASTER-PERFIL.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1300-OBT-MASTER-PERFIL.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1300-OBT-MASTER-PERFIL-USER' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           INITIALIZE ARCL2505-COMMAREA REPLACING NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                             ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES.

           MOVE ARCV8010-GUSERNAME         TO ARCL2505-CUSERID.

           CALL ARCL2505-ROTINA USING ETCL0002-COMMAREA
                                      ARCL2505-COMMAREA.

           IF NOT ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
              MOVE ETCL0002-IND-ERROS
                TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                TO ARCV8011-CPERFIL-S
              MOVE ETCL0002-ST-ERRO
                TO ARCV8011-CPERFIL-MSG
              MOVE ARCK0002-CAPLIC-AR
                TO ARCV8011-CPERFIL-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

       1300-OBT-MASTER-PERFIL-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                PERFORM 2100-OBTEM-DADOS
                   THRU 2199-OBTEM-DADOS-EXIT
           END-IF
           .
       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2100-OBTEM-DADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2100-OBTEM-DADOS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2100-OBTEM-DADOS        ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'ARCV8010-GUSERNAME      ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  ARCV8010-GUSERNAME        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE ARCV8010-GUSERNAME
             TO ARCD0103-GUSERNAME

           EXEC SQL
                 SELECT
                       GUSERNAME
                     , CNOME
                     , CFUNCAO
                     , CPERFIL
                     , CLINGUA
                     , GPASSWORD
                     , ISTATUS
                     , CEMPRESA
                     , CCENTRO
                     , CMOED
                     , MCUSTMED
                     , DDATINI
                     , DDATFIM
                     , CUSERID
                     , HTIMEST
                     , GEMAIL
                     , CTIPOUTIL
                 INTO
                       :ARCD0103-GUSERNAME
                     , :ARCD0103-CNOME
                     , :ARCD0103-CFUNCAO
                     , :ARCD0103-CPERFIL
                     , :ARCD0103-CLINGUA
                     , :ARCD0103-GPASSWORD
                     , :ARCD0103-ISTATUS
                     , :ARCD0103-CEMPRESA
                     , :ARCD0103-CCENTRO
                     , :ARCD0103-CMOED
                     , :ARCD0103-MCUSTMED
                     , :ARCD0103-DDATINI
                     , :ARCD0103-DDATFIM
                     , :ARCD0103-CUSERID
                     , :ARCD0103-HTIMEST
                     , :ARCD0103-GEMAIL
                     , :ARCD0103-CTIPOUTIL
                 FROM ARVT0103
                 WHERE
                   UPPER(GUSERNAME) = UPPER(:ARCD0103-GUSERNAME)
           END-EXEC


           MOVE CON-ARVT0100
             TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2100-OBTEM-DADOS - DEPOI' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'ARCD0103-GUSERNAME '      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(2)
              MOVE  ARCD0103-GUSERNAME        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              MOVE 'SQLWARN0                ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(3)
              MOVE  SQLWARN0                  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(3)

              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 IF VIAL0001-CRIACAO
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO ARCV8011-GUSERNAME-S
                    MOVE ARCK0001-GUSERNAME-EXISTS
                      TO ARCV8011-GUSERNAME-MSG
                 ELSE
                    MOVE ARCD0103-GUSERNAME
                      TO ARCV8011-GUSERNAME
                    MOVE ARCD0103-CNOME
                      TO ARCV8011-CNOME
                    MOVE ARCD0103-CFUNCAO
                      TO ARCV8011-CFUNCAO
                    MOVE ARCD0103-CTIPOUTIL
                      TO ARCV8011-CTIPOUTIL
                    MOVE ARCD0103-CPERFIL
                      TO ARCV8011-CPERFIL
                    MOVE ARCD0103-CLINGUA
                      TO ARCV8011-CLINGUA
                    MOVE ARCD0103-CEMPRESA
                      TO ARCV8011-CEMPRESA
                    MOVE ARCD0103-GEMAIL
                      TO ARCV8011-GEMAIL
                    MOVE ARCD0103-ISTATUS
                      TO ARCV8011-ISTATUS
                    MOVE ARCD0103-DDATINI
                      TO ARCV8011-DDATINI
                    MOVE ARCD0103-DDATFIM
                      TO ARCV8011-DDATFIM
                    IF NOT VIAL0001-VISUALIZACAO
                       IF ARCD0103-ISTATUS = ARCK0002-INACTIVE-STATUS
                          MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                            TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                          MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                            TO ARCV8011-GUSERNAME-S
                          MOVE ARCK0001-GUSERNAME-CANC
                            TO ARCV8011-GUSERNAME-MSG
                       END-IF
                    END-IF
                 END-IF
              ELSE
                 IF NOT VIAL0001-CRIACAO
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO ARCV8011-GUSERNAME-S
                    MOVE ARCK0001-GUSERNAME-N-EXISTS
                      TO ARCV8011-GUSERNAME-MSG
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2199-OBTEM-DADOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.

           MOVE ARCV8011-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE ARCV8011-LENGTH            TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE ARCV8011-NR-CAMPOS         TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE ZEROES
             TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.

       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
           COPY VIAP0015.
           COPY VIAP0016.
      *==============================================================
